          ]
        ]
      },
      {
        "block_label": "text",
        "block_content": "The result is shown in Table 1. Our method achieves high performance, surpassing several baseline algorithms in most setups, and does not require access to the internal structure of the model. This demonstrates that our algorithm is highly effective and robust.",
